z, Armin Shimerman, Brent Spiner, Tom Virtue and Wil Wheaton.</i><br><br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1567110615i/28070621._SY540_.jpg" width="400" height="500" alt="description" class="gr-hostedUserImg"></span>
