<span id="freeTextContainer9171573616472670739">Wells sort of made a bet and wanted to have it covered both ways: in which shape will Apocalypse come?<br/> <br/>Humanity wiped out by super-humans ruling over invincible machines?<br/><br/>Or wiped out by a tiny bacteria?<br/><br/>Choose your ending! And enjoy a vintage science fiction writer while you wait ...</span>

